  "id": "BIT-discourse-2026-32951",
  "summary": "Discourse: Authorization bypass in oneboxer via user-controlled category id",
  "details": "Discourse is an open-source discussion platform. From versions 2026.1.0 to before 2026.1.3, and 2026.2.0 to before 2026.2.2, an authenticated user can obtain shared draft topic titles by sending an inline onebox request with a category_id parameter matching the shared drafts category. This issue has been patched in versions 2026.1.3, 2026.2.2, and 2026.3.0.",
